prometheus doesn't mix metadata with metric names
but it does poll at a scraping interval value, then apply timestamp
+ you never loose data, just preceision
- target discovery
- short lived jobs
- Heroku/NATed systems

prometheus is intented to run in the same network as services (if you can't, look away)
grafana works with prometheus now

prediction alerts (ALERT DiskWillFillIn4Hours)
